          </svg>
        </span>
        <p class="hiw-step__title">Donors fund the pool</p>
        <p class="hiw-step__desc">
          Every donation adds to a community funding pool. Your money
          waits to be paired with verified impact — nothing disappears.
        </p>
        <div class="hiw-step__connector">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-step">
        <p class="hiw-step__num">02</p>
        <span class="hiw-step__icon" aria-hidden="true">
