        <span class="hiw-step__tag">Pending Approval — credits earned after verified attendance</span>
        <div class="hiw-step__connector">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-step">
        <p class="hiw-step__num">04</p>
        <span class="hiw-step__icon">
          <img src="/images/checkin.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="width: 30px; height: 30px; display: block;">
        </span>
        <p class="hiw-step__title">Show up. Check in.</p>
        <p class="hiw-step__desc">
          Simple QR code scan to check-in on arrival. Your contribution goes on record.
          The organizer knows you're there.
        </p>
        <div class="hiw-step__connector">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-step hiw-step--final">
        <p class="hiw-step__num">05</p>
        <span class="hiw-step__icon">
          <i class="fas fa-coins hiw-coins-icon hiw-coins-icon--step" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </span>
        <p class="hiw-step__title">Verification closes the loop</p>
        <p class="hiw-step__desc">
          One organizer tap: Impact Credits post to volunteer wallet.
          Donor attribution receipt updates. Impact report logs
          automatically.
        </p>
        <span class="hiw-step__tag">This is the moment everything connects</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hiw-pullquote">
      <p>One tap. Verified. Everyone knows what happened — for the first time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

